Actions.Text: REFERRED TO CORPORATIONS, AUTHORITIES AND COMMISSIONS

Title: Renames the Winthrop street subway station in the borough of Brooklyn to the SUNY Downstate at Winthrop Avenue station; and provides for the repeal of such provisions upon expiration thereof
Summary: Renames the Winthrop street subway station on the IRT Nostrand Avenue Line of the NYC subway, located in the borough of Brooklyn, to the SUNY Downstate at Winthrop Avenue station.
ActClause: AN ACT directing the metropolitan transportation authority to rename the Winthrop street subway station in the borough of Brooklyn to the SUNY Downstate at Winthrop Avenue station; and providing for the repeal of such provisions upon expiration thereof
